@startuml class_diagram
!theme plain
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam classFontSize 12

title About Page — Domain Model

class AboutContent {
    +AboutContentId: Guid
    +Heading: String
    +Body: String
    +BodyHtml: String
    +ProfileImageId: Guid?
    +CreatedAt: DateTime
    +UpdatedAt: DateTime
    +Version: int
}

class DigitalAsset {
    +DigitalAssetId: Guid
    +StoredFileName: String
    +ContentType: String
    +AltText: String?
}

AboutContent "0..1" --> "0..1" DigitalAsset : profileImage

note right of AboutContent
  Singleton — at most one row exists.
  UpsertAboutContentHandler uses
  GetCurrentAsync; creates if null.
  Body stores raw Markdown source.
  BodyHtml is pre-rendered at save time.
end note

@enduml
